---
import Bio from '../components/Bio.astro';
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = 'About';
const description = 'About my blog.';
const permalink = `${Astro.site.href}about`;
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} permalink={permalink} current="about">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <Bio />
    <br />
    <br />
    <figure class="about-image">
      <img src="/assets/about-illustration.png" alt="Illustration of a notebook" width="400">
    </figure>
    <p>Thank you for taking the time to visit my corner on the Internet.</p>
    <p>This is where I share my passion for technology, with a particular focus on coding and data science. <br/><br/>My primary area of interest?<br/> Music—so it’s no surprise that it takes center stage here. </p>
    <p>Whether you’re here to learn something new, find inspiration, or simply enjoy some thought-provoking content, <br/>I hope you’ll leave with a fresh perspective.</p>
    <p>Check out my <a href="/blog/hello-world">hello world article</a> to learn more.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-image {
    float: right;
    margin: -3em -7em 2em 2em;
    max-width: 300px;
  }

  .about-image img {
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5em;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1020px) {
    .about-image {
      float: none;
      margin: 0 auto 2em;
    }
  }
</style>
